{"tid":926612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拜金既女仔究竟會唔會用真心對朋友","createTime":"2018-12-03T14:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T20:04:18.000Z","uid":213033,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"193610394d1cbde04e6b702431cdb15726ee2f64","tid":926612,"uid":213033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"成堆女仔由細識到大 <br />\n個個(除左A)屋企環境都算曾俊華式中產 <br />\n細個一齊咩顧慮都無 hehe haha過日晨 <br />\n依家大個左 A拜金到仆街<br />\n成日叫我介紹身邊d投行仔或者有錢仔朋友佢識<br />\n依家已經分唔清佢係真心朋友定係為左利益<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鍾意買靚野好多絲都可以明白<br />\n但其實用左個貴d既袋 影多左幾張靚相<br />\n係唔會令一個人突然間變成係有錢人 係女神 係上等人<br />\n<br />\n女仔自己肯努力 心地好 腳踏實地 <br />\n你唔係cat girl咁撚樣 已經可以好charming <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奉勸大家一句 咪撚拜金 自己努力做好自己好過啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf5b0088835595297ca0ac202086449b6d7a515","tid":926612,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"cd78d9d8f806ea7a9a6c2f00266681feae83ab53","tid":926612,"uid":64374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec29236a3f49f959dfc32f230d53a4db9d01a9e9","tid":926612,"uid":35712,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"生活迫無計 你自已曾俊華式中產係香港基層個種苦你又點知"},{"pid":"ca6d5d69ec4e9b4ab25dd4c6eb8289271fca3b1c","tid":926612,"uid":213033,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ec29236a3f49f959dfc32f230d53a4db9d01a9e9","tid":926612,"uid":35712,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"生活迫無計 你自已曾俊華式中產係香港基層個種苦你又點知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-0